170
00:19:25,987 --> 00:19:27,009
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak,...</font>

171
00:19:27,593 --> 00:19:28,598
<font color="#00ff00">...sebab ini.</font>

172
00:19:31,242 --> 00:19:32,308
