173
00:19:36,756 --> 00:19:38,795
<font color="#00ff00">Tak guna!</font>

174
00:19:59,236 --> 00:20:01,137
<font color="#00ff00">Pemikiran tenang.</font>

175
00:20:16,686 --> 00:20:19,413
<font color="#00ff00">Kami sedang mengkaji semua
