193
00:20:58,644 --> 00:20:59,800
<font color="#00ff00">Dan saya petik.</font>

194
00:21:00,452 --> 00:21:02,351
<font color="#00ff00">Bagi Homo-Neanderthalis,...</font>

195
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:04,623
<font color="#00ff00">...sepupu mutannya, spesies primat...</font>

196
00:21:05,142 --> 00:21:06,372
<font color="#00ff00">...yang mana adalah kita.</font>

197
00:21:06,587 --> 00:21:08,469
<font color="#00ff00">Adalah suatu penyimpangan...</font>

198
00:21:08,578 --> 00:21:12,029
<font color="#00ff00">...yang kedatangan spesies manusia
