207
00:21:41,681 --> 00:21:43,854
<font color="#00ff00">Sekarang, perang itu tercetus
di jalan-jalan kita,...</font>

208
00:21:43,922 --> 00:21:46,175
<font color="#00ff00">...bandar kita, rumah kita...</font>

209
00:21:46,251 --> 00:21:50,344
<font color="#00ff00">...dan apabila anda sedar
betapa pentingnya program saya,...</font>

210
00:21:50,752 --> 00:21:52,540
<font color="#00ff00">...pasti sudah terlambat...</font>

211
00:21:53,111 --> 00:21:57,607
<font color="#00ff00">...dan anda akan kalah dalam
dua perang sepanjang hidup anda.</font>

212
00:22:00,554 --> 00:22:02,656
<font color="#00ff00">Maafkan kami, Dr. Trask,...</font>

213
00:22:03,157 --> 00:22:05,336
<font color="#00ff00">...tapi program sentinel anda,...</font>

214
00:22:06,163 --> 00:22:08,117
<font color="#00ff00">...kami tidak akan meluluskan.</font>

215
00:22:20,775 --> 00:22:21,775
<font color="#00ff00">Boleh saya bantu, kolonel?</font>

216
00:22:22,009 --> 00:22:24,110
<font color="#00ff00">Saya mahu lepaskan tentera
