218
00:22:27,948 --> 00:22:29,483
<font color="#00ff00">Berundur, askar.</font>

219
00:22:29,985 --> 00:22:31,818
<font color="#00ff00">Ini arahan.</font>

220
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:42,711
<font color="#00ff00">Senang diri!</font>

221
00:22:43,130 --> 00:22:44,130
<font color="#00ff00">Duduk.</font>

222
00:23:07,833 --> 00:23:08,921
<font color="#00ff00">Apa semua ini?</font>

223
00:23:09,021 --> 00:23:10,490
<font color="#00ff00">Laporan makmal, ujian darah.</font>

224
00:23:10,991 --> 00:23:12,563
<font color="#00ff00">Semua sudah dikemaskan
dan sedia dihantar.</font>

225
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:13,612
<font color="#00ff00">Dihantar ke mana?</font>

226
00:23:13,694 --> 00:23:15,014
<font color="#00ff00">Tempat sama seperti biasa.</font>

227
00:23:15,475 --> 00:23:16,819
<font color="#00ff00">Perusahaan Trask.</font>

228
00:23:18,466 --> 00:23:19,666
<font color="#00ff00">Mari pergi, tuan-tuan.</font>

229
00:23:20,091 --> 00:23:22,354
<font color="#00ff00">Saya akan bawa anda pergi
