235
00:23:33,779 --> 00:23:35,614
<font color="#00ff00">...jalankan beberapa lagi ujian.</font>

236
00:23:41,467 --> 00:23:42,695
<font color="#00ff00">Orang awak bukanlah tentera.</font>

237
00:23:44,132 --> 00:23:45,102
<font color="#00ff00">Pengawal pribadi.</font>

238
00:23:45,627 --> 00:23:47,360
<font color="#00ff00">Kami diberi kuasa untuk
