241
00:23:58,469 --> 00:24:00,426
<font color="#00ff00">Malangnya saya ada kuasa, nak.</font>

242
00:24:01,019 --> 00:24:02,474
<font color="#00ff00">Maafkan saya, awak siapa?</font>

243
00:24:02,831 --> 00:24:04,319
<font color="#00ff00">Persoalannya, mejar...</font>

244
00:24:08,714 --> 00:24:09,581
<font color="#00ff00">Awak siapa?</font>

245
00:24:55,217 --> 00:24:56,061
<font color="#00ff00">Raven!</font>

246
00:24:56,659 --> 00:24:57,965
<font color="#00ff00">Itu bukan nama saya.</font>

247
00:25:04,475 --> 00:25:05,695
<font color="#00ff00">Saya boleh uruskan.</font>

248
00:25:05,698 --> 00:25:06,574
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tahu.</font>

249
00:25:08,637 --> 00:25:10,541
<font color="#00ff00">Mari kita gerak.
Ayuh, mari pergi.</font>

250
00:25:10,766 --> 00:25:11,875
<font color="#00ff00">Mana Erik?</font>

251
00:25:12,101 --> 00:25:13,246
<font color="#00ff00">Saya gerak sendiri sekarang.</font>

252
00:25:16,672 --> 00:25:18,046
<font color="#00ff00">Mari pergi, gerak!</font>

253
00:25:36,617 --> 00:25:38,225
<font color="#00ff00">Hentikan pesawat itu!</font>

254
00:25:38,804 --> 00:25:42,025
<font color="#00ff00">Kita tak boleh tinggalkan
mereka di tempat teruk ini.</font>

255
00:25:42,028 --> 00:25:42,885
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, tuan!</font>

256
00:25:43,596 --> 00:25:45,297
<font color="#00ff00">Awak tak ikut?</font>

257
00:25:45,789 --> 00:25:47,186
<font color="#00ff00">Perang saya belum habis.</font>

258
00:25:47,305 --> 00:25:49,045
<font color="#00ff00">Musuh masih berlegar di luar sana.</font>

259
00:26:12,190 --> 00:26:14,429
<font color="#00ff00">Mana mereka pergi? Empat prebet
