260
00:26:14,434 --> 00:26:15,939
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka sedang menuju ke Tarmac.</font>

261
00:27:14,921 --> 00:27:16,002
<font color="#00ff00">Boleh saya bantu?</font>

262
00:27:17,253 --> 00:27:19,067
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, kenapa dengan sekolah ini?</font>

263
00:27:19,365 --> 00:27:22,241
<font color="#00ff00">Sekolah dah ditutup bertahun lepas.
Awak ayah penuntut?</font>

264
00:27:22,765 --> 00:27:25,169
<font color="#00ff00">Bukan.
Awak siapa?</font>

265
00:27:25,370 --> 00:27:27,296
<font color="#00ff00">Saya Hank. Hank McCoy.</font>

266
00:27:27,302 --> 00:27:29,128
<font color="#00ff00">Saya penjaga rumah ini sekarang.</font>

267
00:27:30,262 --> 00:27:31,478
<font color="#00ff00">Awak Beast?</font>

268
00:27:31,486 --> 00:27:34,002
<font color="#00ff00">Tengoklah awak.
Rasanya awak lambat berkembang.</font>

269
00:27:34,010 --> 00:27:36,856
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tak faham apa awak maksudkan,
saya terpaksa minta awak beredar.</font>

270
00:27:37,867 --> 00:27:38,927
<font color="#00ff00">Mana profesor?</font>

271
00:27:38,930 --> 00:27:40,239
<font color="#00ff00">Tiada profesor di sini.</font>

272
00:27:40,241 --> 00:27:42,335
<font color="#00ff00">Awak agak kuat untuk
seorang budak kurus kering.</font>

273
00:27:42,443 --> 00:27:44,986
<font color="#00ff00">Tolonglah, awak pasti Beast
kecil tiada dalam sana?</font>

274
00:27:44,989 --> 00:27:46,701
<font color="#00ff00">- Tolonglah, Beast.
- Dia tiada di sini.</font>

275
00:27:46,704 --> 00:27:48,059
<font color="#00ff00">- Tolonglah, Beastie.
- Tidak.</font>

276
00:27:49,285 --> 00:27:50,105
<font color="#00ff00">Hei.</font>

277
00:27:51,546 --> 00:27:52,923
<font color="#00ff00">Saya cakap sekolah ini ditutup.</font>

278
00:27:52,929 --> 00:27:55,166
<font color="#00ff00">- Awak perlu pergi.
- Tidak selagi belum jumpa Profesor.</font>

279
00:27:55,170 --> 00:27:57,261
<font color="#00ff00">Tiada profesor di sini,
saya dah beritahu awak.</font>

280
00:27:57,519 --> 00:28:01,204
