281
00:28:03,479 --> 00:28:05,447
<font color="#00ff00">Cuma awak belum tahu.</font>

282
00:28:07,935 --> 00:28:09,157
<font color="#00ff00">Profesor!</font>

283
00:28:15,767 --> 00:28:16,937
<font color="#00ff00">Profesor!</font>

284
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,589
<font color="#00ff00">Hank?</font>

285
00:28:33,841 --> 00:28:35,349
<font color="#00ff00">Apa sedang berlaku di sini?</font>

286
00:28:36,922 --> 00:28:37,731
<font color="#00ff00">Profesor?</font>

287
00:28:38,009 --> 00:28:39,448
<font color="#00ff00">Tolong jangan panggil saya begitu.</font>

288
00:28:39,453 --> 00:28:40,902
<font color="#00ff00">Kenapa, awak kenal dia?</font>

289
00:28:41,009 --> 00:28:43,354
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, nampak macam bukan asing.</font>

290
00:28:43,454 --> 00:28:45,552
<font color="#00ff00">Turunlah dari lampu gantung, Hank.</font>

291
00:28:47,522 --> 00:28:48,788
<font color="#00ff00">Awak boleh berjalan?</font>

292
00:28:49,057 --> 00:28:49,957
<font color="#00ff00">Awak seorang yang peka.</font>

293
00:28:50,425 --> 00:28:51,265
<font color="#00ff00">Saya ingatkan Erik...</font>

294
00:28:51,268 --> 00:28:54,472
<font color="#00ff00">Peliknya, awak gagal faham tanda pada
pintu masuk kami semasa ke sini.</font>

295
00:28:54,478 --> 00:28:58,657
<font color="#00ff00">Ini tanah peribadi, kawan dan saya terpaksa
minta dia arahkan awak untuk beredar.</font>

296
00:29:00,401 --> 00:29:02,102
<font color="#00ff00">Malangnya saya tak boleh, sebab...</font>

297
00:29:04,634 --> 00:29:06,106
<font color="#00ff00">Sebab saya dihantar
