319
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:53,911
<font color="#00ff00">Mahu saya teruskan?</font>

320
00:29:55,563 --> 00:29:56,867
<font color="#00ff00">Saya belum pernah
ceritakan kepada sesiapa.</font>

321
00:29:56,959 --> 00:30:00,598
