<font color="#00ff00">Kami perlu bantuan awak.</font>

326
00:30:18,712 --> 00:30:20,646
<font color="#00ff00">Rasanya saya perlu bangun sekarang.</font>

327
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:27,967
<font color="#00ff00">Apa kaitan Raven dalam masalah ini?</font>

328
00:30:31,891 --> 00:30:33,177
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Jadi, awak cakap...</i></font>

329
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:36,145
<font color="#00ff00">...sekiranya mereka gunakan
kuasa Raven, apa pula seterusnya?</font>

330
00:30:36,271 --> 00:30:38,530
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka jadikan dia senjata?</font>

331
00:30:38,658 --> 00:30:39,747
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

332
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:41,933
<font color="#00ff00">Raven sangat unik.</font>

333
00:30:42,167 --> 00:30:44,029
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, dia memang unik, Hank.</font>

334
00:30:44,245 --> 00:30:47,233
<font color="#00ff00">Pada mulanya,
sentinel cuma menyerang mutan.</font>

335
00:30:47,237 --> 00:30:50,145
<font color="#00ff00">Kemudian mereka berjaya mengesan
genetik pada bukan-mutan...</font>

336
00:30:51,395 --> 00:30:54,863
<font color="#00ff00">...yang akan mempunyai
anak-anak dan cucu mutan.</font>

337
00:30:54,866 --> 00:30:58,584
<font color="#00ff00">Ramai manusia cuba bantu kami,
