ramai orang kita.</font>

1029
01:27:58,626 --> 01:28:00,528
<font color="#00ff00">Hentikan dia, Charles.
Masuki fikirannya.</font>

1030
01:28:00,725 --> 01:28:01,988
<font color="#00ff00">Dia tidak izinkan saya masuk.</font>

1031
01:28:02,357 --> 01:28:05,473
<font color="#00ff00">Saya sukar untuk bertahan,
saya belum cukup kuat lagi.</font>

1032
01:28:13,645 --> 01:28:15,411
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tahu apa yang dilakukan Trask,...</font>

1033
01:28:15,961 --> 01:28:18,069
<font color="#00ff00">...tapi dengan membunuhnya
tidak akan mengembalikan mereka.</font>

1034
01:28:18,845 --> 01:28:19,903
<font color="#00ff00">Itu akan membawa awak ke jalan...</font>

1035
01:28:20,003 --> 01:28:22,001
<font color="#00ff00">...yang tiada arah untuk kembali.</font>

1036
01:28:22,715 --> 01:28:24,524
<font color="#00ff00">Terperangkap dalam kitaran
saling membunuh tanpa berpenghujung.</font>

1037
01:28:24,557 --> 01:28:28,356
<font color="#00ff00">Kita dan mereka,
sehingga tiada yang selamat.</font>

1038
01:28:29,268 --> 01:28:33,036
<font color="#00ff00">Tapi kita boleh halang dia,
sekarang juga, awak dan saya.</font>

1039
01:28:34,158 --> 01:28:36,897
<font color="#00ff00">Awak cuma perlu pulang.</font>

1040
01:28:38,422 --> 01:28:39,963
<font color="#00ff00">Saya terpaksa lakukan.</font>

1041
01:28:40,631 --> 01:28:42,434
<font color="#00ff00">Awak takkan pernah berubah, Charles.</font>

1042
01:28:43,388 --> 01:28:44,233
<font color="#00ff00">Seperti yang saya cakap,...</font>

1043
01:28:44,661 --> 01:28:46,887
<font color="#00ff00">...saya tahu apa yang
sedang saya lakukan.</font>

1044
01:29:02,384 --> 01:29:03,372
<font color="#00ff00">Mana dia?</font>

1045
01:29:03,612 --> 01:29:06,016
<font color="#00ff00">Dia di lapangan terbang
menaiki pesawat.</font>

1046
01:29:06,222 --> 01:29:07,622
<font color="#00ff00">Pesawat menuju ke mana?</font>

1047
01:29:10,592 --> 01:29:12,392
<font color="#00ff00">Washington DC.</font>

1048
01:29:14,053 --> 01:29:17,628
<font color="#00ff00">Hei, ada sesuatu yang saya
nak tunjukkan pada kamu.</font>

1049
01:29:20,057 --> 01:29:21,857
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kita kembali ke masa lampau.</i></font>

1050
01:29:22,036 --> 01:29:23,566
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tetapkan sistem yang saya bina...</font>

1051
01:29:23,568 --> 01:29:26,741
<font color="#00ff00">...untuk merakam berita tentang
Paris pada setiap tiga rangkaian...</font>

1052
01:29:26,748 --> 01:29:27,951
<font color="#00ff00">...dan PBS.</font>

1053
01:29:28,267 --> 01:29:30,061
<font color="#00ff00">Ketiga-tiga? Wow.</font>

1054
01:29:30,276 --> 01:29:31,844
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, dan PBS.</font>

1055
01:29:32,992 --> 01:29:34,290
<font color="#00ff00">Tengoklah apa yang saya jumpa.</font>

1056
01:29:34,538 --> 01:29:37,837
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Esok, di hadapan rumah putih,
presiden akan membuat pengumuman.</i></font>

1057
01:29:37,938 --> 01:29:40,000
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Beliau bersama menteri
pertahanan, Laird...</i></font>

1058
01:29:40,270 --> 01:29:43,925
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...turut meminta bantuan dari
saintis terkenal, Bolivar Trask,...</i></font>

1059
01:29:44,112 --> 01:29:47,135
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...penasihat khas beliau dalam
memerangi isu mutan ini.</i></font>

1060
01:29:47,165 --> 01:29:48,563
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Pihak rumah putih meminta...</i></font>

1061
01:29:48,701 --> 01:29:49,761
<font color="#00ff00">Raven belum sedar tapi...</font>

1062
01:29:50,008 --> 01:29:52,109
<font color="#00ff00">...kalau dia bunuh Trask
dalam acara seperti itu...</font>

1063
01:29:52,112 --> 01:29:53,871
<font color="#00ff00">...dengan disaksikan seluruh dunia...</font>

1064
01:29:55,162 --> 01:29:57,543
<font color="#00ff00">Bermakna kedatangan saya
cuma akan sia-sia.</font>

1065
01:29:58,241 --> 01:30:00,380
<font color="#00ff00">Dan ada lagi berita buruk,
saya melihat laporan.</font>

1066
01:30:00,720 --> 01:30:02,663
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka telah jumpa darah
Raven di Paris.</font>

1067
01:30:02,832 --> 01:30:05,657
<font color="#00ff00">Apa yang kita tahu sekarang,
DNA Raven ada pada mereka.</font>

1068
01:30:05,879 --> 01:30:07,099
<font color="#00ff00">Itulah yang mereka perlu...</font>

1069
01:30:07,108 --> 01:30:08,957
<font color="#00ff00">Untuk mencipta sentinel
pada masa hadapan.</font>

1070
01:30:12,677 --> 01:30:14,725
<font color="#00ff00">Terdapat teori dalam fizik tentang...</font>

1071
01:30:14,843 --> 01:30:16,306
<font color="#00ff00">...masa yang tidak dapat diubah.</font>

1072
01:30:16,735 --> 01:30:18,340
<font color="#00ff00">Seperti sungai,
awak lontar batu ke dalam...</font>

1073
01:30:18,347 --> 01:30:21,959
<font color="#00ff00">...sehingga ada percikan, tetapi aliran
sungai akan kembali seperti sedia-kala.</font>

1074
01:30:22,800 --> 01:30:26,444
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak kiralah apa tindakan awak,
sungai tetap mengalir ke arah sama.</font>

1075
01:30:26,963 --> 01:30:28,320
<font color="#00ff00">Apa yang awak sedang maksudkan?</font>

1076
01:30:28,399 --> 01:30:29,666
<font color="#00ff00">Saya sedang maksudkan,...</font>

1077
01:30:30,491 --> 01:30:31,965
<font color="#00ff00">...macam mana kalau perang
ini tidak dapat dielak?</font>

1078
01:30:32,163 --> 01:30:34,468
<font color="#00ff00">Macam mana kalau Raven
ditakdirkan membunuh Trask?</font>

1079
01:30:36,237 --> 01:30:38,432
<font color="#00ff00">Macam mana kalau inilah
dia yang sebenar?</font>

1080
01:30:40,610 --> 01:30:44,548
<font color="#00ff00">Cuma kerana seseorang
hilang haluan hidupnya,...</font>

1081
01:30:44,935 --> 01:30:46,608
<font color="#00ff00">...tidak bermakna yang dia
akan sesat selama-lamanya.</font>

1082
01:30:51,703 --> 01:30:53,816
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tak percaya teori itu, Hank.</font>

1083
01:30:55,231 --> 01:30:58,144
<font color="#00ff00">Dan saya tak boleh percaya yang
itulah dia yang sebenar.</font>

1084
01:30:59,951 --> 01:31:00,870
<font color="#00ff00">Sediakan pesawat.</font>

1085
01:31:00,879 --> 01:31:02,995
<font color="#00ff00">Kita ke Washington.</font>

1086
01:32:21,448 --> 01:32:22,601
<font color="#00ff00">Awak tak apa-apa?</font>

1087
01:32:22,864 --> 01:32:24,078
<font color="#00ff00">Saya makin baik.</font>

1088
01:32:28,808 --> 01:32:31,449
<font color="#00ff00">Walau apa yang berlaku hari ini,
awak perlu janji pada saya.</font>

1089
01:32:32,310 --> 01:32:35,616
<font color="#00ff00">Awak dah masuki fikiran saya dan
melihat banyak kejadian buruk, tapi...</font>

1090
01:32:36,314 --> 01:32:37,649
<font color="#00ff00">...awak turut melihat kebaikan.</font>

1091
01:32:39,151 --> 01:32:40,526
<font color="#00ff00">X-Men.</font>

1092
01:32:42,000 --> 01:32:43,420
<font color="#00ff00">Janjilah pada saya,
awak akan cari kami semua.</font>

1093
01:32:45,438 --> 01:32:47,327
<font color="#00ff00">Gunakan kuasa awak,
satukan kami semua.</font>

1094
01:32:48,099 --> 01:32:50,121
<font color="#00ff00">Pimpinlah kami, bimbing kami.</font>

1095
01:32:51,596 --> 01:32:54,364
<font color="#00ff00">Storm, Scott.</font>

1096
01:32:56,649 --> 01:32:58,036
<font color="#00ff00">Jean.</font>

1097
01:32:59,336 --> 01:33:01,304
<font color="#00ff00">Ingatlah nama-nama itu.</font>

1098
01:33:02,511 --> 01:33:04,774
<font color="#00ff00">Ada ramai jumlah kita.</font>

1099
01:33:05,555 --> 01:33:07,776
<font color="#00ff00">Kami akan perlukan awak, profesor.</font>

1100
01:33:10,780 --> 01:33:13,148
<font color="#00ff00">Saya akan lakukan yang terbaik.</font>

1101
01:33:13,449 --> 01:33:14,983
<font color="#00ff00">Itu sangat baik.</font>

1102
01:33:16,920 --> 01:33:18,485
<font color="#00ff00">Percayalah pada saya.</font>

1103
01:33:42,634 --> 01:33:45,089
<font color="#00ff00">12 kapal pengangkut menghampiri,
10 batu!</font>

1104
01:33:46,312 --> 01:33:47,446
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka dah jumpa kita.</font>

1105
01:34:04,113 --> 01:34:06,436
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ribuan orang ramai
berkumpul di sini hari ini,...</i></font>

1106
01:34:06,439 --> 01:34:07,928
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...mereka datang dari seluruh dunia...</i></font>

1107
01:34:08,031 --> 01:34:10,295
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...untuk menyaksikan sejarah,
bersama krew berita...</i></font>

1108
01:34:10,297 --> 01:34:12,379
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...dari sekurang-kurangnya
50 negara yang berbeza.</i></font>

1109
01:34:14,064 --> 01:34:15,276
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih.</font>

1110
01:34:17,808 --> 01:34:19,045
<font color="#00ff00">Minta tunjukkan jemputan anda?</font>

1111
01:34:20,002 --> 01:34:21,173
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, tentulah.</font>

1112
01:34:21,514 --> 01:34:22,564
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka berdua bersama saya.</font>

1113
01:34:22,566 --> 01:34:23,510
<font color="#00ff00">Sila masuk.</font>

1114
01:34:23,515 --> 01:34:24,652
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih.</font>

1115
01:34:31,572 --> 01:34:32,685
<font color="#00ff00">Logan!</font>

1116
01:34:32,960 --> 01:34:34,489
<font color="#00ff00">Ikut sini, tuan.</font>

1117
01:35:01,363 --> 01:35:03,304
<font color="#00ff00">Saya belum jumpa dia lagi,
tentu dia berada di sini.</font>

1118
01:35:03,512 --> 01:35:05,198
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Presiden Amerika Syarikat.</i></font>

1119
01:35:27,884 --> 01:35:29,517
<font color="#00ff00">Rakyat Amerika,...</font>

1120
01:35:29,939 --> 01:35:34,408
<font color="#00ff00">...hari ini kita berhadapan
ancaman terbesar dalam sejarah kita,...</font>

1121
01:35:34,508 --> 01:35:35,604
<font color="#00ff00">...mutan.</font>

1122
01:35:38,911 --> 01:35:41,218
<font color="#00ff00">Kami telah menyediakan
persediaan terhadap ancaman ini.</font>

1123
01:35:44,364 --> 01:35:47,953
<font color="#00ff00">Memetik kata-kata dari
Robert Oppenheimer.</font>

1124
01:35:48,160 --> 01:35:49,198
<font color="#00ff00">Pandanglah!</font>

1125
01:35:50,027 --> 01:35:52,530
<font color="#00ff00">Dunia tidak akan pernah sama lagi!</font>

1126
01:36:23,136 --> 01:36:24,188
<font color="#00ff00">Boleh saya bantu?</font>

1127
01:36:27,447 --> 01:36:28,652
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, awak tak boleh.</font>

1128
01:37:06,301 --> 01:37:07,898
<font color="#00ff00">Mereka datang.</font>

1129
01:37:14,658 --> 01:37:16,375
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ini untuk kamu,
saudara dan saudariku.</i></font>

1130
01:37:18,898 --> 01:37:19,691
<font color="#00ff00">Raven?</font>

1131
01:37:22,745 --> 01:37:23,679
<font color="#00ff00">Saya jumpa dia.</font>

1132
01:37:24,468 --> 01:37:25,768
<font color="#00ff00">Lepaskan saya, Charles.</font>

1133
01:37:27,917 --> 01:37:29,306
<font color="#00ff00">Dia di sana. Kamu nampak?</font>

1134
01:37:29,417 --> 01:37:30,643
<font color="#00ff00">Agen rahsia,...</font>

1135
01:37:30,743 --> 01:37:31,719
<font color="#00ff00">...di sebelah kiri pentas.</font>

1136
01:37:31,727 --> 01:37:32,973
<font color="#00ff00">- Dapat.
- Pergi.</font>

1137
01:37:53,837 --> 01:37:55,041
<font color="#00ff00">Apa awak sedang buat?</font>

1138
01:37:55,229 --> 01:37:56,635
<font color="#00ff00">Saya belum arahkan awak
mengaktifkan mereka.</font>

1139
01:37:56,731 --> 01:37:57,901
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tak aktifkan.</font>

1140
01:38:16,461 --> 01:38:18,680
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Raven, tolonglah dengar
kata-kata saya.</i></font>

1141
01:38:18,992 --> 01:38:22,942
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kita telah diberi peluang kedua
untuk menentukan siapa diri kita.</i></font>

1142
01:38:25,082 --> 01:38:26,303
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Jangan lakukan.</i></font>

1143
01:38:29,853 --> 01:38:32,041
<font color="#00ff00">Tuan-tuan, anda tidak dibenarkan
melepasi kawasan ini.</font>

1144
01:38:39,978 --> 01:38:41,745
<font color="#00ff00">Kita tak mampu hentikan
jumlah sebanyak itu.</font>

1145
01:38:41,851 --> 01:38:44,523
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, tapi kita boleh
lengahkan mereka.</font>

1146
01:39:22,712 --> 01:39:24,316
<font color="#00ff00">Erik!</font>

1147
01:40:09,106 --> 01:40:09,880
<font color="#00ff00">Storm!</font>

1148
01:40:29,192 --> 01:40:30,692
<font color="#00ff00">Pergi! Pergi! Pergi!</font>

1149
01:40:46,721 --> 01:40:47,604
<font color="#00ff00">Lekas, pergi!</font>

1150
01:40:47,614 --> 01:40:49,357
<font color="#00ff00">Bawa kami ke DEFCON 3.</font>

1151
01:40:49,417 --> 01:40:52,160
<font color="#00ff00">- En. Presiden, kita dalam ancaman.
- Macam mana pertahanan udara kita?</font>

1152
01:40:52,166 --> 01:40:53,599
<font color="#00ff00">Pertahanan udara telah dipersiapkan.</font>

1153
01:40:53,603 --> 01:40:55,132
<font color="#00ff00">Apa yang sedang berlaku?</font>

1154
01:40:55,139 --> 01:40:56,132
<font color="#00ff00">Saya akan betulkan ini.</font>

1155
01:40:56,232 --> 01:40:57,327
<font color="#00ff00">Itulah yang awak cakap sebelum ini!</font>

1156
01:40:57,530 --> 01:40:58,692
<font color="#00ff00">Saya mahu keluarkan kenyataan.</font>

1157
01:40:58,696 --> 01:41:01,113
<font color="#00ff00">Sekarang seluruh dunia tahu yang
kita tidak mampu lindungi mereka!</font>

1158
01:41:01,463 --> 01:41:02,680
<font color="#00ff00">Saya akan betulkan ini.</font>

1159
01:41:02,831 --> 01:41:04,498
<font color="#00ff00">Betulkanlah!</font>

1160
01:42:16,085 --> 01:42:17,003
<font color="#00ff00">Charles!</font>

1161
01:43:06,175 --> 01:43:07,762
<font color="#00ff00">Semua orang selamat?</font>

1162
01:43:41,716 --> 01:43:42,600
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak!</font>

1163
01:43:43,379 --> 01:43:44,808
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak!</font>

1164
01:43:46,580 --> 01:43:47,519
<font color="#00ff00">Belakang awak!</font>

1165
01:44:32,157 --> 01:44:33,304
<font color="#00ff00">Sekarang!</font>

1166
01:44:56,921 --> 01:44:59,701
<font color="#00ff00">Mungkin saya tidak sepatutnya
tanya begini, tapi...</font>

1167
01:44:59,925 --> 01:45:02,479
<font color="#00ff00">...di masa depan, saya selamat?</font>

1168
01:45:03,027 --> 01:45:03,785
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak.</font>

1169
01:45:06,005 --> 01:45:07,342
<font color="#00ff00">Tapi kita boleh ubah,...</font>

1170
01:45:07,624 --> 01:45:08,797
<font color="#00ff00">...kan?</font>

1171
01:45:19,651 --> 01:45:21,380
<font color="#00ff00">Lakukan tugas awak.</font>

1172
01:45:30,568 --> 01:45:32,121
<font color="#00ff00">Awak di mana?</font>

1173
01:45:49,411 --> 01:45:51,030
<font color="#00ff00">Saya uruskan! Pergi!</font>

1174
01:46:33,684 --> 01:46:35,055
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, tuhan, tidak.</font>

1175
01:46:51,061 --> 01:46:53,316
<font color="#00ff00">Awak takkan jadi seorang
yang bertahan hidup lagi.</font>

1176
01:47:35,949 --> 01:47:37,043
<font color="#00ff00">Salah seorang dari
mereka ada dalam sini.</font>

1177
01:47:39,760 --> 01:47:41,887
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, tidak, tidak!
Jangan bunuh dia.</font>

1178
01:47:42,342 --> 01:47:43,276
<font color="#00ff00">Saya perlukan dia hidup-hidup.</font>

1179
01:47:56,915 --> 01:47:58,223
<font color="#00ff00">Apa sedang berlaku?</font>

1180
01:49:06,148 --> 01:49:08,299
<font color="#00ff00">Kamu bina senjata itu
untuk musnahkan kami.</font>

1181
01:49:09,396 --> 01:49:10,467
<font color="#00ff00">Kenapa?</font>

1182
01:49:14,699 --> 01:49:17,246
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kerana anda takut terhadap
kemampuan kami.</i></font>

1183
01:49:18,170 --> 01:49:20,679
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kerana kami berbeza.</i></font>

1184
01:49:22,007 --> 01:49:25,115
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Manusia sentiasa gerun
terhadap sesuatu yang berbeza.</i></font>

1185
01:49:25,991 --> 01:49:27,294
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Saya di sini untuk
maklumkan kepada anda,...</i></font>

1186
01:49:27,554 --> 01:49:28,926
<font color="#00ff00">...maklumkan kepada seluruh dunia,...</font>

1187
01:49:29,848 --> 01:49:32,023
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...anda memang patut takut kami.</i></font>

1188
01:49:32,450 --> 01:49:34,145
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kamilah masa hadapan.</i></font>

1189
01:49:34,967 --> 01:49:37,332
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kami yang akan mewarisi dunia ini.</i></font>

1190
01:49:37,922 --> 01:49:39,932
<font color="#00ff00">Dan sesiapa saja yang halang kami...</font>

1191
01:49:39,940 --> 01:49:42,379
<font color="#00ff00">...akan menanggung nasib sama
seperti orang-orang ini...</font>

1192
01:49:42,383 --> 01:49:43,905
<font color="#00ff00">...yang sedang anda saksikan di sini.</font>

1193
01:49:51,202 --> 01:49:54,180
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Hari ini diaturkan untuk
menunjukkan kuasa anda...</i></font>

1194
01:49:54,719 --> 01:49:56,856
<font color="#00ff00">...sebaliknya, saya
memberi anda gambaran...</font>

1195
01:49:56,938 --> 01:50:00,412
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...terhadap kemusnahan yang mampu
dilepaskan kaum saya terhadap anda.</i></font>

1196
01:50:09,791 --> 01:50:11,897
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Biarlah ini menjadi
peringatan kepada dunia...</i></font>

1197
01:50:12,645 --> 01:50:15,442
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...dan kepada saudara-saudari
mutan saya di luar sana.</i></font>

1198
01:50:16,182 --> 01:50:17,461
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ini kata saya...</i></font>

1199
01:50:18,287 --> 01:50:19,750
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...tiada lagi bersembunyi,...</i></font>

1200
01:50:20,081 --> 01:50:21,870
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...tiada lagi penderitaan.</i></font>

1201
01:50:22,890 --> 01:50:25,216
<font color="#00ff00">Anda hidup dalam bayangan
dan perasaan malu...</font>

1202
01:50:25,316 --> 01:50:27,653
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...serta ketakutan untuk terlalu lama.</i></font>

1203
01:50:27,685 --> 01:50:28,809
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Keluarlah.</i></font>

1204
01:50:29,478 --> 01:50:30,870
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Mari bersama saya.</i></font>

1205
01:50:30,876 --> 01:50:34,240
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Berjuanglah bersama dalam
persaudaraan kaum kita.</i></font>

1206
01:50:35,009 --> 01:50:36,543
<font color="#00ff00">Hari esok yang baru.</font>

1207
01:50:37,878 --> 01:50:39,512
<font color="#00ff00">Bermula hari ini.</font>

1208
01:50:47,019 --> 01:50:48,710
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Saban tahun terbuang sia-sia...</i></font>

1209
01:50:48,921 --> 01:50:50,755
<font color="#00ff00">...dengan berperang
sesama sendiri, Charles.</font>

1210
01:50:54,389 --> 01:50:57,061
<font color="#00ff00">Saya mahu detik itu kembali.</font>

1211
01:51:36,850 --> 01:51:38,040
<font color="#00ff00">- En. Presiden.
- Berundur.</font>

1212
01:51:38,050 --> 01:51:39,674
<font color="#00ff00">Saya cakap, berundur!</font>

1213
01:51:41,803 --> 01:51:43,370
<font color="#00ff00">Awak nak buat kenyataan?</font>

1214
01:51:43,939 --> 01:51:45,806
<font color="#00ff00">Bunuhlah saya. Tiada masalah.</font>

1215
01:51:45,834 --> 01:51:47,808
<font color="#00ff00">Tapi ampunilah yang lain.</font>

1216
01:52:00,415 --> 01:52:02,561
<font color="#00ff00">Sangat berani, En. Presiden...</font>

1217
01:52:03,366 --> 01:52:04,809
<font color="#00ff00">...tapi awak tidak berniat...</font>

1218
01:52:04,816 --> 01:52:06,710
<font color="#00ff00">...untuk mengampuni mana-mana dari kami.</font>

1219
01:52:07,381 --> 01:52:10,514
<font color="#00ff00">Masa depan golongan kami
bermula sekarang.</font>

1220
01:52:46,029 --> 01:52:47,329
<font color="#00ff00">Awak seorang penembak pakar dulu.</font>

1221
01:52:47,335 --> 01:52:48,675
<font color="#00ff00">Percayalah, saya masih pakar.</font>

1222
01:53:02,370 --> 01:53:03,998
<font color="#00ff00">Keluar dari kepala saya, Charles!</font>

1223
01:53:04,217 --> 01:53:05,361
<font color="#00ff00">Raven.</font>

1224
01:53:05,815 --> 01:53:07,857
<font color="#00ff00">Tolonglah, jangan sampai
kita bermusuh hari ini.</font>

1225
01:53:07,864 --> 01:53:09,817
<font color="#00ff00">Pandanglah sekeliling awak,
kita memang musuh.</font>

1226
01:53:10,292 --> 01:53:11,883
<font color="#00ff00">Bukan semua daripada kita.</font>

1227
01:53:12,329 --> 01:53:14,389
<font color="#00ff00">Apa yang awak
dah lakukan sejauh ini...</font>

1228
01:53:14,626 --> 01:53:16,962
<font color="#00ff00">...adalah menyelamatkan
nyawa mereka semua.</font>

1229
01:53:17,858 --> 01:53:20,245
<font color="#00ff00">Awak boleh tunjukkan kepada
mereka jalan yang lebih baik.</font>

1230
01:53:24,064 --> 01:53:25,183
<font color="#00ff00">Hentikan dia, Charles.</font>

1231
01:53:27,703 --> 01:53:31,218
<font color="#00ff00">Saya dah cuba kawal awak semenjak
hari pertama kita jumpa,...</font>

1232
01:53:31,704 --> 01:53:33,715
<font color="#00ff00">...dan lihatlah akibatnya.</font>

1233
01:53:35,875 --> 01:53:38,436
<font color="#00ff00">Semua yang berlaku sekarang...</font>

1234
01:53:39,237 --> 01:53:41,282
<font color="#00ff00">...dalam genggaman awak.</font>

1235
01:53:45,510 --> 01:53:48,622
<font color="#00ff00">Saya sentiasa percayakan awak, Raven.</font>

1236
01:55:27,044 --> 01:55:28,944
<font color="#00ff00">Dia milik awak, Charles.</font>

1237
01:55:56,738 --> 01:55:59,452
<font color="#00ff00">Kalau awak biar mereka tangkap saya,
pasti saya akan mati.</font>

1238
01:55:59,514 --> 01:56:00,640
<font color="#00ff00">Awak tahu itu.</font>

1239
01:56:01,534 --> 01:56:02,747
<font color="#00ff00">Saya tahu.</font>

1240
01:56:05,260 --> 01:56:06,887
<font color="#00ff00">Selamat tinggal, kawan lama.</font>

1241
01:56:09,450 --> 01:56:11,050
<font color="#00ff00">Selamat tinggal, Erik.</font>

1242
01:56:44,882 --> 01:56:46,786
<font color="#00ff00">Pasti awak nak lepaskan mereka?</font>

1243
01:56:47,740 --> 01:56:48,923
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

1244
01:56:49,783 --> 01:56:51,435
<font color="#00ff00">Saya menaruh harapan terhadap mereka.</font>

1245
01:56:52,657 --> 01:56:56,509
<font color="#00ff00">Masanya akan tiba, Hank,
untuk kita bersatu.</font>

1246
01:57:00,530 --> 01:57:02,153
<font color="#00ff00">Macam mana dengan Logan?</font>

1247
01:58:18,208 --> 01:58:21,376
<font color="#00ff00">Buckminster Fuller adalah
contoh arkitek menakjubkan...</font>

1248
01:58:21,381 --> 01:58:25,651
<font color="#00ff00">...dengan seni bina yang menyerupai
bayangan kita terhadap masa hadapan.</font>

1249
01:58:31,915 --> 01:58:34,541
<font color="#00ff00">Selamat pagi, Logan.
Permulaan lewat.</font>

1250
01:58:44,759 --> 01:58:46,114
<font color="#00ff00">Pergilah makan tengah hari.</font>

1251
01:58:46,288 --> 01:58:47,388
<font color="#00ff00">Bagus.</font>

1252
01:58:47,757 --> 01:58:49,168
<font color="#00ff00">Sangat bagus.</font>

1253
01:58:50,074 --> 01:58:51,173
<font color="#00ff00">Storm.</font>

1254
01:59:22,572 --> 01:59:23,812
<font color="#00ff00">Jean.</font>

1255
01:59:25,142 --> 01:59:26,217
<font color="#00ff00">Hei, Logan.</font>

1256
01:59:29,033 --> 01:59:30,369
<font color="#00ff00">Awak okey?</font>

1257
01:59:32,332 --> 01:59:33,357
<font color="#00ff00">Awak di sini.</font>

1258
01:59:34,347 --> 01:59:36,109
<font color="#00ff00">Di mana lagi saya patut berada?</font>

1259
01:59:40,625 --> 01:59:42,287
<font color="#00ff00">Tenang, kawan.</font>

1260
01:59:44,114 --> 01:59:46,549
<font color="#00ff00">Ada perkara yang memang
tidak pernah berubah.</font>

1261
01:59:48,080 --> 01:59:49,551
<font color="#00ff00">Gembira jumpa awak, Scott.</font>

1262
01:59:52,555 --> 01:59:53,889
<font color="#00ff00">Jumpa lagi, Jean.</font>

1263
01:59:58,174 --> 01:59:59,673
<font color="#00ff00">Profesor.</font>

1264
01:59:59,889 --> 02:00:02,893
<font color="#00ff00">Logan, semua lancar?</font>

1265
02:00:06,205 --> 02:00:07,522
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

1266
02:00:08,831 --> 02:00:10,432
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, rasanya begitulah.</font>

1267
02:00:27,099 --> 02:00:28,213
<font color="#00ff00">Awak berjaya.</font>

1268
02:00:28,704 --> 02:00:29,699
<font color="#00ff00">Berjaya apa?</font>

1269
02:00:29,831 --> 02:00:31,899
<font color="#00ff00">Logan, bukannya awak
ada kelas untuk diajar?</font>

1270
02:00:32,388 --> 02:00:34,436
<font color="#00ff00">Kelas untuk diajar?</font>

1271
02:00:35,100 --> 02:00:36,294
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, sejarah.</font>

1272
02:00:36,991 --> 02:00:37,922
<font color="#00ff00">Sejarah?</font>

1273
02:00:39,276 --> 02:00:40,998
<font color="#00ff00">Sebenarnya, saya perlu bantuan
terhadap sejarah.</font>

1274
02:00:41,402 --> 02:00:43,118
<font color="#00ff00">Bantuan dengan apa?</font>

1275
02:00:43,191 --> 02:00:47,109
<font color="#00ff00">Peristiwa yang berlaku
selepas tahun 1973.</font>

1276
02:00:51,137 --> 02:00:54,536
<font color="#00ff00">Rasanya sejarah yang
saya tahu sedikit berbeza.</font>

1277
02:00:55,874 --> 02:00:57,816
<font color="#00ff00">Selamat kembali.</font>

1278
02:01:00,309 --> 02:01:01,941
<font color="#00ff00">Gembira jumpa awak, Charles.</font>

1279
02:01:03,406 --> 02:01:05,130
<font color="#00ff00">Gembira dapat jumpa semua orang.</font>

1280
02:01:05,417 --> 02:01:06,644
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

1281
02:01:07,491 --> 02:01:09,558
<font color="#00ff00">Saya ada janji
yang harus ditunaikan.</font>

1282
02:01:10,799 --> 02:01:14,039
<font color="#00ff00">Kita berdua ada banyak
perkara untuk dibincangkan.</font>

1283
02:01:14,905 --> 02:01:15,865
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

1284
02:01:20,007 --> 02:01:22,453
<font color="#00ff00">Apa perkara terakhir yang awak ingat?</font>

1285
02:01:27,277 --> 02:01:28,888
<font color="#00ff00">Tenggelam.</font>

1286
02:01:37,772 --> 02:01:38,914
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Masa lampau.</i></font>

1287
02:01:40,128 --> 02:01:43,091
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Dunia baru yang tidak menentu.</i></font>

1288
02:01:54,497 --> 02:01:56,990
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Dunia dengan kemungkinan
tanpa kesudahan.</i></font>

1289
02:02:00,124 --> 02:02:01,700
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Dan akibat yang tidak terhingga.</i></font>

1290
02:02:03,444 --> 02:02:04,536
<font color="#00ff00">Alamak!</font>

1291
02:02:04,542 --> 02:02:06,087
<font color="#00ff00">Dia masih hidup!</font>

1292
02:02:10,503 --> 02:02:13,332
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Pilihan yang tidak terkira
nilainya menentukan takdir kita.</i></font>

1293
02:02:14,138 --> 02:02:16,554
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Setiap pilihan, setiap peristiwa.</i></font>

1294
02:02:16,757 --> 02:02:19,058
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Adalah percikan di sungai masa.</i></font>

1295
02:02:19,523 --> 02:02:21,758
<font color="#00ff00">Apa kita akan lakukan
pada dia, Mejar Stryker?</font>

1296
02:02:21,953 --> 02:02:23,808
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Percikan yang cukup...</i></font>

1297
02:02:24,017 --> 02:02:26,260
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...dan anda akan mampu
mengubah air pasang.</i></font>

1298
02:02:26,760 --> 02:02:27,959
<font color="#00ff00">Saya ambil alih dari sini.</font>

1299
02:02:28,064 --> 02:02:31,853
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kerana masa hadapan tidak
pernah mampu ditentukan.</i></font>

1300
